                            <comment id="17317968" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 9 Apr 2021 13:09:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Perhaps we should have padded this enum out, the way we do in ApplicationState to avoid these kinds of errors in mixed versions.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
